<lb n="0019a03" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0019a0301">入王宮時見大臣。時行軍中時逢怨對。時見
<lb n="0019a04" ed="T"/>毒蛇毒龍。時遇夜叉毘舍遮羅剎烏&CB00425;娑摩
<lb n="0019a05" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0019002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囉＝羅【三】</note><note n="0019002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囉＝羅【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0019002"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">羅</rdg></app>所魅時。乃至山海險難中時。如是怖
<lb n="0019a06" ed="T"/>畏悉皆解脫。</p>
<lb n="0019a07" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0019a0701" type="dharani">曩謨<note place="inline">引</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合引</note>&CB00718;婆&CB00085;室羅<note place="inline">二合引</note>野&CB00718;<note place="inline">一</note>呬&CB00619;
<lb n="0019a08" ed="T"/>呬&CB00619;<note place="inline">二</note>唧&CB00619;唧&CB00619;<note place="inline">三</note>迦<note place="inline">引</note>播&CB00619;<note place="inline">四</note>摩<note place="inline">引</note>鄧霓娑&CB00085;
<lb n="0019a09" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引五</note></p>
<lb n="0019a10" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0019a1001">又復王法所執或被枷鎖杻械牢固其身。一
<lb n="0019a11" ed="T"/>切枉橫憂苦逼切悉皆解脫。</p>
<lb n="0019a12" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0019a1201" type="dharani">曩謨<note place="inline">引</note>多<note place="inline">引</note>哩<note place="inline">引</note>多<note place="inline">引</note>哩<note place="inline">引一</note>烏哆<note place="inline">引</note>哩<note place="inline">引二</note>&CB00418;哩
<lb n="0019a13" ed="T"/><note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引三</note></p>
<lb n="0019a14" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0019a1401">又復星曜所持。或惡夢變怪致諸病苦夭枉
<lb n="0019a15" ed="T"/>至死。乃至&CB00508;諍論理互相恐逼。如是諸怖悉
<lb n="0019a16" ed="T"/>皆解脫。</p>
