<lb n="0019b05" ed="T"/>夜&CB00085;&CB00344;&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>切<note place="inline">四</note>尾夢贊底<note place="inline">五</note>呬&CB00619;唧&CB00619;<note place="inline">六</note>迦
